{"tid":677330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林忌開心大發現: 百度釋liberty為「無禮冒昧」係奧威爾式胡說八道","createTime":"2018-05-25T05:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T13:21:53.000Z","uid":76115,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6ad3435fa90ff7f168d2fdf6b463bfb218ed28","tid":677330,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"福佳與林忌創作<br />\n<br />\n咩叫「奧威爾式的胡說八道(Orwellian nonsense)」？望下CCTVB翻譯Donald Trump 講 Liberty 做「特權」就知，查下百度，就會搵到中國人把 Liberty 譯做「放肆、無禮、有權的、擅自、冒昧」，完全就係奧威爾在 1984/動物農莊內篡改字義的劇情<br />\n<br />\n想知點解CCTVB新聞會把Liberty譯做「特權」？百度幫到你！捉姦在床，CCTVB新聞就係中國控制！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/31960462_2170627536295696_9119257627258257408_n.png?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=9a0861127ea990eb4da7e02e10d608bc&amp;oe=5B81D3D6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F31960462_2170627536295696_9119257627258257408_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D9a0861127ea990eb4da7e02e10d608bc%26oe%3D5B81D3D6&h=0345d08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fokguyhk/posts/2170628202962296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguyhk%2Fposts%2F2170628202962296&d=ZVrugfLkI%2B5%2F78SZCSYSStU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7157ca25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fokguyhk/posts/2170628202962296</a><br />\n<br />\n屌那星好撚柒, 仲要cap哂圖間哂線懶係技術性擊倒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日扮哂崇英菁英連liberty有無禮之行一解都唔識, 本土派靠呢啲kol唔怪得愈做愈柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/liberty_1?q=liberty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com%2Fdefinition%2Fenglish%2Fliberty_1%3Fq%3Dliberty&d=ZVrugfLkI%2B5%2F78SZCSYSStU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=58910c14\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/liberty_1?q=liberty</a><br />\n[singular] an act or a statement that may offend or annoy somebody, especially because it is done without permission or does not show respect <br />\nHe took the liberty of reading my files while I was away. <br />\nThey've got a liberty, not even sending me a reply."},{"pid":"17aced45931fdc6db3a83a6b61bd7cda6bfd1133","tid":677330,"uid":113626,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:58:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/zht/%E8%A9%9E%E5%85%B8/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E/liberty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdictionary.cambridge.org%2Fzht%2F%25E8%25A9%259E%25E5%2585%25B8%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AA%259E%2Fliberty&d=ZVrugfLkI%2B5%2F78SZCSYSStU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=98a0b264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dictionary.cambridge.org/zht/%E8%A9%9E%E5%85%B8/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E/liberty</a><br />\n<br />\nliberty noun (BAD BEHAVIOUR)<br />\n​<br />\n[ C ] an example of speech or behaviour that upsets other people because it shows little respect or does not follow what is thought to be polite or acceptable:<br />\n<br />\nWhat a liberty, to refuse the invitation on your behalf, without even asking you!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次先再幫你推, 今次太7"},{"pid":"ad2409ada031ef72b08acedb62e2e1eea9d8730b","tid":677330,"uid":113626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來都唔知呢條友咩料<br />\n<br />\n2007年，林忌因敬仰梁美芬學養而入讀神大法律博士(JD)，希望成為四大護法的再傳弟子，可惜當2008年讀憲法學時鼠王芬已因做了香港立法會議員而不上堂，拜入梁美芬門下美夢成空。<br />\n<br />\n大佬原來讀JD英文都可以咁好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b964268e54036788ffa75ced9227a665e059c7d","tid":677330,"uid":76115,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:02:17.000Z","msg":"查下百度，就會搵到中國人把 Liberty 譯做「放肆、無禮、有權的、擅自、冒昧」，<br />\n<br />\ncctvb錯譯柒係一件事, 但係睇佢呢句, 佢似乎係覺得liberty真係只有自由一解<br />\n佢一係英文好撚屎, 一係覺得自己乜都識哂唔使求證, 一係蠢撚過隻豬, 一係all of the above, 最撚可憐係仲有好多港豬鍾意上佢個page一齊幻想自己係高等人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3c9612d3fce19ab625edea19afa973c025e2da","tid":677330,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"柒"},{"pid":"a4998503c580c9e8b2c92dde3dc3c945d249b500","tid":677330,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad2409ada031ef72b08acedb62e2e1eea9d8730b","tid":677330,"uid":113626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來都唔知呢條友咩料<br />\n<br />\n2007年，林忌因敬仰梁美芬學養而入讀神大法律博士(JD)，希望成為四大護法的再傳弟子，可惜當2008年讀憲法學時鼠王芬已因做了香港立法會議員而不上堂，拜入梁美芬門下美夢成空。<br />\n<br />\n大佬原來讀JD英文都可以咁好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"咩u grad?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651e4e63f0d1f9addd4b75e273379aa90e64a038","tid":677330,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"comment section班自我感覺良好港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nVincent Poon 越睇越合理，只因翻譯的員工，完全無接觸過(個人的)自由、(天地)造物者的觀念。信唔信係一件事，香港長大冇理由唔知Liberty、creator 。<br />\n突然覺得好人類學。<br />\n<br />\nRaymond Lee 1984 <strong>new speak</strong>: &quot;War is Peace, Freedom is Slavery, Ignorance is Strength&quot;<br />\n<br />\n(<strong>Newspeak</strong>精髓就係在於兩個字要合埋......)<br />\n<br />\nJoey in Hong Kong Statue of Liberty 放肆无礼解放像<br />\n<br />\nEdward Au Fact check 過，原來百真係將liberty解作放肆無禮。心血來潮check 下freedom,百度解作特權。<br />\n果然大家活係平行宇宙。 🙏🏻阿門<br />\n<br />\nHei Wrong Lee 其實Cambridge個到有寫明係at liberty 而at liberty 呢句係片語 phrase 要好似中文詞語咁成個解架<br />\n<br />\n(唔使片語, 就咁單數liberty都可作無禮之行)"},{"pid":"f9a1e00909c415f8ef1bb04e6c3f6f9fc1a8050d","tid":677330,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6426854e8e28cb5f3fe3097afc00fc00ba2dd24","tid":677330,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48fe247fdd0622e5be532d7bc4e634e39f641c6","tid":677330,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"成班五毛打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a65abf192a66db355da5026bd87fdf1a8befbd","tid":677330,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a48fe247fdd0622e5be532d7bc4e634e39f641c6","tid":677330,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"成班五毛打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"1c42c5e40f33d3d49c7b76ea7b1df69c1f557226","tid":677330,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a04753504ee5e6352b3520a4c4de77074735830","tid":677330,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a48fe247fdd0622e5be532d7bc4e634e39f641c6","tid":677330,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"成班五毛打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:16:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/zht/詞典/英語-漢語-繁體/liberty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdictionary.cambridge.org%2F